#: reports/Partner-Report/content/_sR.yaml:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Your severe infection rates (BSI, and HAP) exceed the reference population's 75th percentile. This requires comprehensive review of surveillance definitions, hand hygiene compliance, environmental cleaning, and other core infection prevention practices.\n"
msgstr "Ihre Raten schwerer Infektionen (BSI und HAP) liegen über dem 75. Perzentil der Referenzpopulation. Dies erfordert eine umfassende Überprüfung der Surveillancedefinitionen, der Einhaltung der Handhygiene, der Reinigung der Räumlichkeiten sowie anderer zentraler Maßnahmen zur Infektionsprävention.\n"

#. type: Hash Value: outlier grouped_severe_infection_rates_low
#: reports/Partner-Report/content/_sR.yaml:1
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Your severe infection rates (BSI, and HAP) exceed the reference population's 75th percentile. This requires comprehensive review of surveillance definitions, hand hygiene compliance, environmental cleaning, and other core infection prevention practices.\n"
msgid "Your severe infection rates (BSI, and HAP) are below the reference population's 25th percentile. This favorable outcome suggests effective implementation of infection prevention strategies and warrants documentation of successful practices.\n"
